column1: Que 1 Understand the distribution of arrival dates, including the most common arrival days and summary statistics for lead times.

column6:
SELECT 
    STR_TO_DATE(CONCAT(arrival_date_year, ' ', arrival_date_week_number, ' 1'), '%X %V %w') AS arrival_date,
    COUNT(*) AS total_arrivals
FROM 
    booking_details
GROUP BY 
    arrival_date
ORDER BY 
    total_arrivals desc;
